<p>Sets the color of the contents of a <link xref="Clutter.Text">Clutter.Text</link> actor.</p><p>The overall opacity of the <link xref="Clutter.Text">Clutter.Text</link> actor will be the
result of the alpha value of @color and the composited
opacity of the actor itself on the scenegraph, as returned
by clutter_actor_get_paint_opacity().</p>

